$SPY $QQQ $AMD $AAPL OH, gees,I just got a tweet, Powell was kiCKED OUT of the same restaurant he treated Trump to dinner 3+ years ago, early Nov. 2018, when meeting over the FOMC about to make aggressive rates moves.

Trump said, &quot;no, Jay, you don&#39;t have to raise rates, inflation is in check &amp; economy weak from China trade war.&quot; 

Jay listened.

Now,  3+ yrs later, 
Biden said, at same restaurant, &quot;C&#39;mon, man, you got to hold off on QE til midterms.&quot; 

Powell replied, &quot; No, sir, inflation grossly different 2018 from now plus economy opposite of weak, to strain matters even more. We&#39;ll see 15% inflation by summer IF we don&#39;t take drastic measures now. Short-term 6 mo. pain now IF huge move now, Joe.&quot; 

Biden, &quot;Ahh, I see, well, gotta go.&quot;

Then, Powell gets the meal bill,  &quot;WHAT THE HECK! I PAID $20 LESS FOR THE EXACT SAME MEAL BACK IN 2018!&quot;
